public static java.lang.String generateXQueryForRNSSearch(java.lang.String retv)

Returns:

generateXQueryForRNSSearch

public static java.lang.String generateXQueryForRNSSearch(java.lang.String retv,
                                                          java.lang.String kvKey)
Generate XQuery String for RNS Search operation. 
 --- Available variables in retv ---
 $ent := /ns1:RNSEntryResponseType
 $name := string($ent/@entry-name)
 $epr := $ent/ns1:endpoint
 $meta := $ent/ns1:metadata
 $sptrns := $meta/ns1:supports-rns

Parameters:
retv - XML (a part of <ns1:metadata> for return value)
kvKey - a key name of RNSKeyValue (not search RNSKeyValue if kvKey is null)
Returns:
Generated XQuery
